flowchart LR
    newPr[/purchase-requests/new/] --> pick[Pick INTERNAL_PRINT subcategory]
    pick --> draft[createPR or update DRAFT]
    draft --> modal[Confirm Print modal]
    modal --> confirm{Confirm?}
    confirm -->|No| draft
    confirm -->|Yes| reserve[reserveSerialRangeForPR]
    reserve --> atomic[atomicReserveSerialRange]
    atomic --> ok{Success?}
    ok -->|No| err[Show error]
    ok -->|Yes| executed[PR EXECUTED_PRINT]
    executed --> printPage[/purchase-requests/id/print/]
    printPage --> export[CSV or label export]

    style newPr fill:#DAE8FC,stroke:#007AD2
    style reserve fill:#DAE8FC,stroke:#007AD2
    style atomic fill:#F0F0F0,stroke:#666666
    style executed fill:#CDF4D3,stroke:#66D575
    style confirm fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#E8A302
    style err fill:#FFCDC2,stroke:#FF7556
